    "asOf": "2020-06-24",
    "date": "2021-08-18T19:11:34Z",
    "text": "Platform Accountability and Consumer Transparency Act or the PACT Act\n\nThis bill requires providers of interactive computer services (e.g., social media platforms) to (1) publish an acceptable use policy, (2) provide a system for users to submit complaints related to the removal of content, and (3) periodically report about violations of the use policy and removal of content."
